com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.model

Class Style

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.model.Style
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.IsSerializable

    public final class Style
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.IsSerializable
    Holds the persistent styling information of a webapp. Instances of Style are created and persisted to the datastore as the result of HTTP POST calls from Google Apps Scripts running in Google Docs to the Rest servlet in Google App Engine.
    Since:
    12-05-2012
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Todd Url , url
